snippet.description:
Here's The Poop That Ended Johnny Depp And Amber Heard's Marriage
Subscribe To InformOverload: http://bit.ly/2xB5CqA

Alright, so if you’ve been following this case, you know that amber heard is being accused of pooping in the bed she shared with johnny.  Depp accused amber heard of pooping in the bed as a prank after ambers 30th birthday party in 2016 after the two of them got in a fight. The housekeeper is the one that took the photos of the poop because she was supposedly so disgusted. Heard blamed it on the dog at the time, but according to the housekeeper, hilda vargas, it was clearly human feces.
